snippet.title: Drugstore Tutorial | Amber Rush L'Oréal Infallible Eyeshadow
snippet.description:
My Instagram! 
http://www.instagram.com/juliedawnolsen
♡ CLICK SHOW MORE ♡ to expand for more info!

♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡

Where I get my Sigma brushes (this is my affiliate link) - http://www.sigmabeauty.com/?Click=470680

Where I get my Real Technique Brushes and Sponge - 
http://www.kohls.com/search.jsp?search=real+techniques&submit-search=web-ta-keyword

Products I used on Camera
Elf Eyeshadow Primer
NYC Smooth Bronzing Face Powder - Sunny
NYX Single Eyeshadow - Whipped Cream (matte white)
L'Oreal La Palette Nude 2 
L'Oreal Infallible Eyeshadow - Amber Rush
NYX Side on Glide on Pencil - Golden Bronze
Elf Black liquid liner 

Products I used off Camera
Maybelline Better Skin Foundation - Nude Beige
Maybelline Better Skin Concealer - Light/Medium
Elf HD under eye setting powder
L'Oreal True Match Super Blendable Powder - Soft Ivory
Anastasia Brow Wiz - Carmel 
L'Oreal Brow Stylist Plumper - Light/Medium 
L'Oreal Infallible Pro Spray & Set 
Tart Lights Camera Lashes Mascara 
Clinique Bottom Lash Mascara 
Wet n Wild Coloricon Bronzer - Ticket to Brazil (bronzer)
Kat Von D Shade + Light - Middle bottom shade (contour)
Maybelline Dream Bouncy Blush - Coffee Cake (blush)
Wet n Wild Coloricon Bronzer - Reserve Your Cabana (highlight)
Rimmel Exaggerate Lip Liner - East End Snob
CoverGirl Jumbo Gloss Balm Cream - Parfait 
Wet n Wild Lipstick - Think Pink (center of lip)  

♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡♡
